3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses a machine learning technique to evaluate the quality of segmentation results, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with 3D medical segmentation tasks, which can be considered as a multimedia application.
